{"tid":1399390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［尋人] 港大同學於葵芳地鐵站被不明中年男子襲擊","createTime":"2019-08-03T07:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:50:07.000Z","uid":268182,"like":873,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":148,"replies":[{"pid":"7af167f360a657bcad422db03f1d8125c366e345","tid":1399390,"uid":268182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:01:21.000Z","msg":"今日，本關注組於葵芳擺設街站時，有同學遭身份不明中年男子襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n該名白衫男子先向街站同學吐口水，及後更於地鐵站內多次推撞關注組義工同學、更以粗口辱罵及恐嚇一個位街坊要「斬你全家」。<br />\n<br />\n有人報警，警察到場了解後，現時受襲同學與該名男子正於葵涌警署協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地以家搵緊頭先被恐嚇嘅個位巴打做証人，如果你見到呢個post，請聯絡香港大學反送中關注組Facebook。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZRF9WD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZRF9WD.png&h=d23752b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457cd332be79e12fb19498ac7f9d0858df45386c","tid":1399390,"uid":154131,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a29048270da4117fd64eaf5c243bd0d4364bdc6","tid":1399390,"uid":240975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ba7bb079eb264d2bb53ec0c60d7f112fe49abf","tid":1399390,"uid":192105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae9b6fe8547028a1dee69e2f9a3681026ee35fa0","tid":1399390,"uid":1632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"fc4d7ead95c5320bc961fcdf51f3ad83c873173f","tid":1399390,"uid":54902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d371a1cdf28333ab077485b47be850dc531dc83b","tid":1399390,"uid":122592,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy"